blog.name: phan-toast
blog.title: Oh dear
blog.description: Michelle • 21 • Send me a message to join my Discord Server!

summary: I don’t know why it’s hitting me now, but we haven’t had a new dnpgames video since 2018. It’s March now. It didn’t seem like...
body:
I don’t know why it’s hitting me now, but we haven’t had a new dnpgames video since 2018. It’s March now. It didn’t seem like that long ago but ouch.

Don’t get me wrong, I’m so happy they (specifically Dan now) are taking a break, and I hope they come back when they feel ready. And if worst case scenario they take years or never come back to the gaming channel? Yeah I’ll be sad but if they think that’s what they need to do it’s their life.

But damn. I miss them.
